'''2014年加州伊斯拉維斯塔槍擊事件'''為发生在美国[[加利福尼亞大學聖塔芭芭拉分校|加利福尼亞大學聖塔芭芭拉分校]]鄰近社區{{link-en|伊斯拉維斯塔|Isla Vista, California|伊斯拉維斯塔}}的连环杀人事件。事件發生在太平洋时间2014年5月23日，凶手先在公寓内刺死3人後，驾车到伊斯拉維斯塔社區冲撞行人并且开枪，致使該社區造成3人死亡、13人受伤。凶手后来在警方交火過程中自殺<ref name="Nguyen">{{cite web|last=Nguyen|first=Daisy|title=7 Dead in Drive-by Shooting Near UC Santa Barbara|url=http://abcnews.go.com/US/wireStory/dead-drive-shooting-uc-santa-barbara-23853689|publisher=ABC News|accessdate=2014-05-24|archive-date=2014-06-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140601003027/http://abcnews.go.com/US/wireStory/dead-drive-shooting-uc-santa-barbara-23853689|dead-url=no}}</ref>。事後肇事者被確認為就讀圣塔芭芭拉城市學院的学生，22歲的艾略特·羅傑<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/answer-sheet/wp/2014/05/25/thousands-hold-vigil-as-uc-santa-barbara-reacts-to-shootings/|title = Thousands hold vigil as UC Santa Barbara reacts to shootings|last = Strauss|first = Valerie|date = 2014-05-25|work = The Washington Post|accessdate = |archive-date = 2016-08-10|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160810060701/https://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/answer-sheet/wp/2014/05/25/thousands-hold-vigil-as-uc-santa-barbara-reacts-to-shootings|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

