三名男子被刺死在攻擊者的公寓。受害人分別為20歲的华裔学生James（洪晟元（Cheng Yuan Hong））；19歲的华裔学生George Chen（陳喬治）以及20歲的华裔学生Weihan David Wang（王偉漢）<ref>[http://abc7.com/news/isla-vista-killing-spree-all-victims-identified/76775/ ISLA VISTA KILLING SPREE: ALL VICTIMS IDENTIFIED] {{Wayback|url=http://abc7.com/news/isla-vista-killing-spree-all-victims-identified/76775/ |date=20140526044356 }}, [[ABC7_News|ABC7 News]], May 25, 2014.</ref><ref>Sernoffsky, Evan. [http://www.sfgate.com/bayarea/article/Three-victims-in-Santa-Barbara-rampage-from-Bay-5504239.php Three victims in Santa Barbara rampage from Bay Area] {{Wayback|url=http://www.sfgate.com/bayarea/article/Three-victims-in-Santa-Barbara-rampage-from-Bay-5504239.php |date=20140527020854 }}, ''[[旧金山纪事报|San Francisco Chronicle]]'', May 25, 2014.</ref>。<br />James與George Chen是攻擊者的室友，警方正在調查Weihan Wang是否也參加室友之間聚會或參觀公寓的殺戮之夜<ref name="autogenerated3">Farnsworth, Ben; Martinez, Alys. [http://www.keyt.com/news/name-of-fourth-mass-murder-victim-revealed/26165132 Name of Fourth Mass Murder Victim Revealed] {{Wayback|url=http://www.keyt.com/news/name-of-fourth-mass-murder-victim-revealed/26165132 |date=20140526092209 }}, {{tsl|en|KEYT||KEYT}}, May 25, 2014.</ref><ref name="USA TODAY" >[http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/usanow/2014/05/24/shooting-california-santa-barbara/9532405/ Police identify Calif. shooting suspect as Elliot Rodger] {{Wayback|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/usanow/2014/05/24/shooting-california-santa-barbara/9532405/ |date=20201030154023 }}, [[今日美國|USA TODAY]], May 24, 2014</ref><ref>Leopold, Todd. [http://www.cnn.com/2014/05/24/us/santa-barbara-shooting-victims/index.html?hpt=hp_t2 Father of rampage victim: 'When will this insanity stop?'] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cnn.com/2014/05/24/us/santa-barbara-shooting-victims/index.html?hpt=hp_t2 |date=20200920010151 }}, [[CNN|CNN]], May 24, 2014.</ref><ref name="7 Dead in 'Mass Murder' Rampage Near UC Santa Barbara">{{Cite web |url=http://www.nbclosangeles.com/news/local/shooting-isla-vista-uc-santa-barbara-260505021.html |title="7 Dead in 'Mass Murder' Rampage Near UC Santa Barbara" |access-date=2014-05-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140525213934/http://www.nbclosangeles.com/news/local/shooting-isla-vista-uc-santa-barbara-260505021.html |archive-date=2014-05-25 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="Sheriffs never saw menacing videos before rampage">{{Cite web |url=http://news.yahoo.com/sheriffs-never-saw-menacing-videos-rampage-204433571.html |title="Sheriffs never saw menacing videos before rampage" |accessdate=2014-05-26 |archive-date=2014-05-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140526064634/http://news.yahoo.com/sheriffs-never-saw-menacing-videos-rampage-204433571.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>"[http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20140527/404899/ 【動新聞】加州校園血案7死　2台生遇害] {{Wayback|url=http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20140527/404899/ |date=20160806105157 }}." ''[[蘋果日報_(香港)|Apple Daily]]''. May 27, 2014. Retrieved on June 14, 2016.</ref>。這三人都是在加州大學聖塔巴巴拉分校（UCSB）唸書的學生<ref name="Thwarted in his plan, California gunman improvised">{{Cite web |url=http://www.cbsnews.com/news/thwarted-in-his-plan-california-gunman-improvised/ |title="Thwarted in his plan, California gunman improvised" |accessdate=2014-05-26 |archive-date=2014-05-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140526032350/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/thwarted-in-his-plan-california-gunman-improvised/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

凶手随后驾车行凶，於聯誼會房子外枪殺22歲的Katherine Cooper和19歲的Veronika Weiss；而20歲的Christopher Michael-Martinez在伊斯拉維斯塔德利超市（Isla Vista Deli Mart）中被枪殺。<ref name="Video Rant, Then Deadly Rampage in California Town">{{Cite web |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2014/05/25/us/california-drive-by-shooting.html |title="Video Rant, Then Deadly Rampage in California Town" |accessdate=2014-05-26 |archive-date=2014-06-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140625064617/http://www.nytimes.com/2014/05/25/us/california-drive-by-shooting.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。另又十三人受傷，其中8人是槍傷，4人是遭受攻擊者的車輛衝撞後外傷，還有1人的傷勢未定<ref name="Santa Barbara shooting rampage ends with 7 fatalities, 13 injured">{{Cite web |url=http://www.chicagotribune.com/news/chi-santa-barbara-shooting-20140524,0,4028820.story |title="Santa Barbara shooting rampage ends with 7 fatalities, 13 injured" |accessdate=2014-05-26 |archive-date=2014-05-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140525195606/http://www.chicagotribune.com/news/chi-santa-barbara-shooting-20140524,0,4028820.story |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

