==肇事者==
肇事嫌疑人被认为是22歲的艾略特‧羅傑<ref name="Video Rant, Then Deadly Rampage in California Town"/><ref name=Telegraph.Shooting/>，他出生在[[英國|英國]][[倫敦|倫敦]]，五歲移居至美國。羅傑成長於[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]。他的母親李欽，是[[馬來西亞|馬來西亞]]华裔<ref name=CNNPB>{{cite news|last=Brown|first=Pamela|title=California killer's parents frantically searched for son during shooting|url=http://cnn.com/2014/05/25/justice/santa-barbara-shooter-parents/index.html|accessdate=2014-05-25|newspaper=CNN|date=2014-05-24|archive-date=2020-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201022215110/https://www.cnn.com/2014/05/25/justice/santa-barbara-shooter-parents/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，他的父親是英裔美國人，美國電影製片人[[彼得‧羅傑|彼得‧羅傑]]，其作品包括在「飢餓遊戲」中擔任第二單元助理导演<ref>{{cite web| last = Flynn| first = Mike| title = Elliot Rodger shootings in Isla Vista, Santa Barbara, California. Elliot Rodger is the son of one of the directors who worked on 'Hunger Games'| accessdate = 2014-05-25| date = 2014-05-25| url = http://www.coveredglobe.com/elliot-rodger-shootings-isla-vista-santa-barbara-california-elliot-rodger-son-one-directors-worked-hunger-games/281714/| deadurl = yes| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140525202046/http://www.coveredglobe.com/elliot-rodger-shootings-isla-vista-santa-barbar| archivedate = 2014年5月25日}}</ref>。他的繼母是演員{{link-en|Soumaya Akaaboune|Soumaya Akaaboune}}<ref name=Telegraph.Shooting/>。他的祖父是攝影記者[[喬治‧羅傑|喬治‧羅傑]]<ref>{{Cite news| last = Sherwell| first = Philip| title = California drive-by shooting: 'Son of Hunger Games assistant director' Elliot Rodger suspected of killing six| accessdate = 2014-05-25| date = 2014-05-24| url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/northamerica/usa/10853875/California-drive-by-shooting-Son-of-Hunger-Games-assistant-director-Elliot-Rodger-suspected-of-killing-six.html| archive-date = 2014-05-25| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140525210142/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/northamerica/usa/10853875/California-drive-by-shooting-Son-of-Hunger-Games-assistant-director-Elliot-Rodger-suspected-of-killing-six.html| dead-url = no}}</ref>。他有一個妹妹和一個年輕的同父異母兄弟<ref name="Inside Santa Barbara Killer's Manifesto">{{Cite web |url=http://abcnews.go.com/US/santa-barbara-killers-friend-lonely-guy/story?id=23860511 |title="Inside Santa Barbara Killer's Manifesto" |accessdate=2014-05-26 |archive-date=2019-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191128200024/https://abcnews.go.com/US/santa-barbara-killers-friend-lonely-guy/story?id=23860511 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。九年級時，艾略特在校被[[霸凌|霸凌]]狀況日漸嚴重，他陳述自己每天都在學校獨自哭泣<ref name=LATimes.Videos/>。在2012年，艾略特說表示自己在這世界上唯一了解他的朋友，在公眾場所上與他斷絕友誼關係，而不給予他任何理由。他在一個健美的網上論壇裡面被描述為“正在醞釀中的連環殺手”，艾略特是该论坛的一個註冊用戶<ref name="California shooting: Elliot Rodger's friends thought he was 'a serial killer in the making'">{{Cite web |url=http://www.mirror.co.uk/news/world-news/california-shooting-elliot-rodgers-friends-3607196 |title="California shooting: Elliot Rodger's friends thought he was 'a serial killer in the making'" |accessdate=2014-05-26 |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111230627/https://www.mirror.co.uk/news/world-news/california-shooting-elliot-rodgers-friends-3607196 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

根據羅傑家庭律師所敘，艾略特是[[亞斯柏格症|亞斯柏格症]]患者<ref>{{cite web|title=Drive-by shooter was 'receiving psychiatric treatment', family confirms|url=http://www.thetimes.co.uk/tto/news/world/americas/article4099469.ece|publisher=The Times (UK)|accessdate=2014-05-24|author=Rankin, David|date=2014-05-24|archive-date=2017-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170306152649/http://www.thetimes.co.uk/tto/news/world/americas/article4099469.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref>，曾接受數名治療師診聊，就讀于聖塔芭芭拉城市學院。但校方表示艾略特已無在校上課<ref name="Suspect in California rampage blamed aloof women">{{Cite web |url=http://news.yahoo.com/suspect-california-rampage-blamed-aloof-women-081618824.html |title="Suspect in California rampage blamed aloof women" |accessdate=2014-05-26 |archive-date=2014-05-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140526022410/https://news.yahoo.com/suspect-california-rampage-blamed-aloof-women-081618824.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。上大學之前，艾略特就讀于名為「{{link-en|Crespi Carmelite High School|Crespi Carmelite High School}}」的男子[[天主教|天主教]]高中，但在畢業前離開了學校。就讀高中時期，艾略特曾遭到校園霸凌，他曾經在睡覺時，被其他同學用膠帶把頭纏繞在書桌上<ref name="Video Rant, Then Deadly Rampage in California Town"/><ref name="Parents read shooting suspect's manifesto too late">{{Cite web |url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/nation/2014/05/25/santa-barbara-shootings-and-stabbings/9565513/ |title="Parents read shooting suspect's manifesto too late" |accessdate=2014-05-26 |archive-date=2014-06-29 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Qhf1iVfh?url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/nation/2014/05/25/santa-barbara-shootings-and-stabbings/9565513/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他曾在[[YouTube|Youtube]]、[[Facebook|Facebook]]以及自己名为 ''Elliot Rodger's Official Blog''的部落格上張貼流露出孤獨與被排擠之情感的貼文。他宣稱自己被規定用許多藥。但其持續用藥時間以及其藥物尚不得而知，而在其自述中称其精神病醫師名為Charles Sophy<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.latimes.com/local/la-me-isla-vista-suspect-20140525-story.html#page=1 |title=Isla Vista shooting suspect's videos reflect cold rage - Los Angeles Times |publisher=Latimes.com |date= |accessdate=2014-05-26 |archive-date=2014-05-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140526014930/http://www.latimes.com/local/la-me-isla-vista-suspect-20140525-story.html#page=1 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.scribd.com/doc/225967704/17/Years-Old |title=22 Years Old for My Twisted World: The Story of Elliot Rodger |publisher=Scribd.com |date= |accessdate=2014-05-26 |archive-date=2014-06-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140603015036/http://www.scribd.com/doc/225967704/17/Years-Old |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===宣言和影片===
他行凶前在网上发表了一百多页的“艾略特·羅傑宣言（Elliot Rodger Manifesto）”<ref>{{cite news|title=Isla Vista shooting suspect's videos reflect cold rage|url=http://www.latimes.com/local/la-me-isla-vista-suspect-20140525-story.html|accessdate=2014-05-25|newspaper=Los Angeles Times|date=2014-05-25|author=Mozingo, Joe|author2=Covarrubias, Amanda|author3=Winton, Richard|archive-date=2014-05-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140526014930/http://www.latimes.com/local/la-me-isla-vista-suspect-20140525-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，详述自己的成长经历，在宣言中他宣称受到极不公平的待遇，对人类绝望，决心报复社会，杀掉那些之前看不起他的人。还发表数段影片，包括“为什麼女生讨厌我（Why Do Girls Hate Me So Much）<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/verify_controversy?next_url=%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DsFAt3ChOsuA |title="为什麼女生讨厌我（Why Do Girls Hate Me So Much）" |accessdate=2020-12-05 |archive-date=2017-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170308121252/https://www.youtube.com/verify_controversy?next_url=%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DsFAt3ChOsuA |dead-url=no }}</ref>”、“艾略特·羅傑的复仇（Elliot Rodger's Retribution）<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/verify_controversy?next_url=%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMQUW3Km01BM%26feature%3Dkp%26bpctr%3D1401166993 |title="艾略特·羅傑的复仇（Elliot Rodger's Retribution）" |accessdate=2020-12-05 |archive-date=2017-03-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170311033841/https://www.youtube.com/verify_controversy?next_url=%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMQUW3Km01BM%26feature%3Dkp%26bpctr%3D1401166993 |dead-url=no }}</ref>”，表示自己孤独和性压抑，受到社会排斥，质疑为何没有女性对其表示好感。

